{"tid":366241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港開埠176年8月20日","createTime":"2017-08-20T00:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T00:29:38.000Z","uid":18245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e5ccf7dc4a4b39541d89cb6fb27d63ccad7350","tid":366241,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:29:38.000Z","msg":"今日全世界都望住香港<br />\n你要Attention 有<br />\n你有人 今日都有<br />\n希望大家好好善用今次既機會 表達自己想表達既野 例如: banner<br />\n唔好聽講句 你今日一怯 無做到你本來想做既野<br />\n將來未必會再有機會比你去做 <br />\n<br />\n同埋好想講 之前見過好多人用<br />\nHong Kong is not China 既banner<br />\n目前香港的確係被殖民 成為中國既領土<br />\n係呢個位 你好難去argue <br />\n<br />\n所以既然你想表達香港唔係中國<br />\n點解唔直接出香港獨立呢<br />\n例如以下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/082338_ea9a4c67b7b7f7776628e4c6c86f0265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F082338_ea9a4c67b7b7f7776628e4c6c86f0265.jpg&h=89678228&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/082340_5d8ee3430b050a1516177e6319e906ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F082340_5d8ee3430b050a1516177e6319e906ac.jpg&h=cb6e469f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/082341_ba931dc3c088adc4af37d6b971297a03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F082341_ba931dc3c088adc4af37d6b971297a03.jpg&h=47d75e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申立場 本人支持香港獨立</span></span>"}]}